WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:00:17.237 --> 00:00:19.781
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Again. a larger ship has arrived.</i></font>

3
00:00:19.865 --> 00:00:23.952
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Today marks the fourth month
since the aliens invaded our world.</i></font>

4
00:00:24.703 --> 00:00:28.499
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Four long months.
The hardest our world has ever known.</i></font>

5
00:00:28.582 --> 00:00:31.919
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We have suffered.
We have sacrificed lives.</i></font>

6
00:00:32.001 --> 00:00:34.379
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>land. loved ones.</i></font>

7
00:00:35.964 --> 00:00:40.177
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And yet. with millions gone.
we here at the World Defense Coalition</i></font>

8
00:00:40.260 --> 00:00:44.598
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>are fighting for you every day
with every resource of every nation.</i></font>

9
00:00:44.681 --> 00:00:49.728
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We are doing everything we can
to understand and overcome our enemy.</i></font>

10
00:00:50.354 --> 00:00:54.775
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We ask for your help.
Please cooperate with the military.</i></font>

11
00:00:54.858 --> 00:00:57.820
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>comply with all codes.
and evacuate contaminated areas.</i></font>

12
00:00:58.403 --> 00:01:02.699
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>The alien spores have now infected the air
in over 30% of our planet.</i></font>

13
00:01:02.783 --> 00:01:06.286
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We have set up shelter for refugees
from all infected areas.</i></font>

14
00:01:06.870 --> 00:01:13.043
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We are working together. one world.
one coalition. to bring you to safety.</i></font>

15
00:01:13.126 --> 00:01:15.337
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Together. we will win this war.</i></font>

16
00:01:16.004 --> 00:01:19.174
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Together. we will see the other side
of these dark days.</i></font>

17
00:01:20.217 --> 00:01:24.429
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And when that sun rises
on a sky free from our invaders.</i></font>

18
00:01:25.430 --> 00:01:29.101
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>it will be the brightest day
our species has ever known.</i></font>

19
00:02:40.964 --> 00:02:44.009
<font color="#FFFFFF">Run! Run!</font>

20
00:04:17.727 --> 00:04:20.355
<font color="#FFFFFF">Don't worry.
we are going to find your mama.</font>

21
00:04:55.849 --> 00:04:58.268
<font color="#FFFFFF">WDC. World Defense?</font>

22
00:04:58.310 --> 00:04:59.853
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're with the Coalition? Government?</font>

23
00:04:59.895 --> 00:05:01.230
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mitsuki Yamato?</font>

24
00:05:01.772 --> 00:05:02.898
<font color="#FFFFFF">There are people here in trouble.</font>

25
00:05:02.940 --> 00:05:04.149
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're not here for them.</font>

26
00:05:04.191 --> 00:05:05.052
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let go of me!</font>

27
00:05:05.067 --> 00:05:06.068
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you saying?</font>

28
00:05:06.109 --> 00:05:08.737
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me go! What are you doing?</font>

29
00:05:09.071 --> 00:05:11.240
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me go! What are you doing?</font>

30
00:05:11.281 --> 00:05:12.991
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to help everyone!</font>

31
00:05:13.033 --> 00:05:17.079
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're the Government! Help everyone!
What are you doing?</font>

32
00:05:17.120 --> 00:05:18.872
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me go!</font>

33
00:05:20.123 --> 00:05:21.625
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me go!</font>

34
00:05:30.092 --> 00:05:31.134
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me down!</font>

35
00:05:31.176 --> 00:05:33.762
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let go of me. Let go of me!</font>

36
00:05:35.347 --> 00:05:36.723
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me down. let me down.</font>

37
00:05:36.765 --> 00:05:37.751
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let go of me.</font>

38
00:05:37.766 --> 00:05:39.810
<font color="#FFFFFF">- We have orders…
- People are dying!</font>

39
00:05:39.852 --> 00:05:41.728
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I understand.
- I have to help them.</font>

40
00:05:41.770 --> 00:05:43.814
<font color="#FFFFFF">We are losing this war.</font>

41
00:05:43.856 --> 00:05:45.274
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me down.</font>

42
00:05:45.315 --> 00:05:46.900
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let me down. people are in trouble
and need our help.</font>

43
00:05:46.942 --> 00:05:49.987
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're taking you somewhere
that could help us win…</font>

44
00:05:53.323 --> 00:05:56.243
<font color="#FFFFFF">…somewhere you could save everyone.</font>

45
00:06:01.748 --> 00:06:03.792
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let go of me. Let go of me.</font>

46
00:06:14.636 --> 00:06:17.097
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where are we going?</font>

47
00:07:35.175 --> 00:07:38.804
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>…attacks in India
are now spreading west into Pakistan.</i></font>

48
00:07:38.887 --> 00:07:41.431
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>creating a refugee crisis
that aid groups are calling</i></font>

49
00:07:41.515 --> 00:07:43.767
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>the worst of the invasion thus far.</i></font>

50
00:07:44.351 --> 00:07:46.770
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>The World Defense Coalition
is reporting ammonia levels</i></font>

51
00:07:46.854 --> 00:07:49.731
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>rising at an alarming rate
round the atmosphere.</i></font>

52
00:07:49.815 --> 00:07:52.651
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>with some areas approaching
200 parts per million.</i></font>

53
00:07:52.734 --> 00:07:54.820
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Supporters from the fringe group.
the Movement.</i></font>

54
00:07:54.903 --> 00:07:57.531
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>have continued to cause problems
for the Coalition.</i></font>

55
00:07:57.614 --> 00:08:01.160
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>This morning. a supply convoy
was ambushed and stripped of rations</i></font>

56
00:08:01.243 --> 00:08:04.496
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>while headed for a survivor's camp
in the… region.</i></font>

57
00:08:04.580 --> 00:08:07.374
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>- Raids of this nature have increased…</i>
- Do you have any candy?</font>

58
00:08:07.457 --> 00:08:09.668
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>- …the food shortage continues to worsen…</i>
- What?</font>

59
00:08:09.751 --> 00:08:12.004
<font color="#FFFFFF">Jell-O? Any ice cream?</font>

60
00:08:12.087 --> 00:08:16.425
<font color="#FFFFFF">Kid. we barely have food.
We stopped getting ice a month ago.</font>

61
00:08:16.508 --> 00:08:18.302
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>…make their way to the nearest camp.</i></font>

62
00:08:32.983 --> 00:08:36.403
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay. then what about stuffed animals?</font>

63
00:08:36.487 --> 00:08:39.697
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like a teddy bear?
It doesn't even have to be a bear.</font>

64
00:08:39.781 --> 00:08:44.119
<font color="#FFFFFF">It can be an otter. a seal.
a rabbit on a key chain…</font>

65
00:08:44.202 --> 00:08:46.455
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey. Who brought you here?</font>

66
00:08:46.538 --> 00:08:48.790
<font color="#FFFFFF">My mommy. She's in the bathroom.</font>

67
00:08:50.959 --> 00:08:51.960
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bathroom?</font>

68
00:09:03.597 --> 00:09:05.390
<font color="#FFFFFF">You need a key for the bathroom.</font>

69
00:09:06.475 --> 00:09:07.476
<font color="#FFFFFF">You wait right there.</font>

70
00:09:08.143 --> 00:09:11.688
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>…Dubai and Santiago
remain largely untouched at this time.</i></font>

71
00:09:11.772 --> 00:09:14.024
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>suggesting that climate
and terrain may play a role.</i></font>

72
00:09:14.107 --> 00:09:15.400
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. we gotta go.</font>

73
00:09:20.155 --> 00:09:22.324
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey!
- Seventeen. sixteen…</font>

74
00:09:31.333 --> 00:09:32.876
<font color="#FFFFFF">Twelve. eleven.</font>

75
00:09:32.960 --> 00:09:34.628
<font color="#FFFFFF">ten. nine…</font>

76
00:09:34.711 --> 00:09:37.381
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey! You. out there!</font>

77
00:09:38.549 --> 00:09:40.384
<font color="#FFFFFF">Eight. seven…</font>

78
00:09:42.094 --> 00:09:44.346
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Where's Luke?
- He was right behind me.</font>

79
00:09:49.059 --> 00:09:51.270
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Open the damn door!
- Where's your brother?</font>

80
00:09:59.153 --> 00:10:02.447
<font color="#FFFFFF">Open the damn door!</font>

81
00:10:22.217 --> 00:10:25.929
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Luke. what happened to you? Are you okay?
- Mom. I got tools. Look.</font>

82
00:10:26.013 --> 00:10:27.806
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. you know the rules.</font>

83
00:10:27.890 --> 00:10:31.059
<font color="#FFFFFF">The moment they move for the door.
you have 17 seconds to get out.</font>

84
00:10:31.143 --> 00:10:32.352
<font color="#FFFFFF">You took more than 30.</font>

85
00:10:32.436 --> 00:10:35.272
<font color="#FFFFFF">You could have died in those seconds.
All of us could have.</font>

86
00:10:35.355 --> 00:10:36.523
<font color="#FFFFFF">But we didn't. okay?</font>

87
00:10:36.607 --> 00:10:39.067
<font color="#FFFFFF">- And we need these.
- Luke. you know the rules!</font>

88
00:10:39.151 --> 00:10:40.777
<font color="#FFFFFF">Seventeen seconds!</font>

89
00:10:41.445 --> 00:10:42.446
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.</font>

90
00:10:45.115 --> 00:10:46.200
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know the rules.</font>

91
00:11:26.073 --> 00:11:28.242
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're almost there.</font>

92
00:11:34.414 --> 00:11:35.999
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's their ship.</font>

93
00:11:38.502 --> 00:11:41.296
<font color="#FFFFFF">the one we shot out of the sky…</font>

94
00:11:45.801 --> 00:11:48.095
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know what it is.</font>

95
00:11:49.763 --> 00:11:51.765
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's coming. Madam President.</font>

96
00:11:51.849 --> 00:11:53.183
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Well. I hope you're right this time.</i></font>

97
00:11:53.267 --> 00:11:55.102
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We've had that ship
for nearly four months now.</i></font>

98
00:11:55.185 --> 00:11:56.854
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And if you can't provide progress fast.</i></font>

99
00:11:56.937 --> 00:11:58.730
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>the Coalition will have
to take over the operation.</i></font>

100
00:11:58.814 --> 00:12:02.442
<font color="#FFFFFF">Might I remind you there wouldn't
be an operation without my funding.</font>

101
00:12:02.526 --> 00:12:06.655
<font color="#FFFFFF">So. technically. it belongs to me.
not some United Nations knockoff.</font>

102
00:12:06.738 --> 00:12:09.158
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>This is not
one of your expensive toys. Nikhil.</i></font>

103
00:12:09.241 --> 00:12:12.035
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>And I'm telling you
what the world leaders are telling me.</i></font>

104
00:12:12.119 --> 00:12:13.162
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>We need results.</i></font>

105
00:12:13.245 --> 00:12:16.290
<font color="#FFFFFF">That map was nearly 80% green last week.</font>

106
00:12:16.373 --> 00:12:17.916
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now we're clinging to 75.</font>

107
00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:19.751
<font color="#FFFFFF">There are dead zones
across whole countries.</font>

108
00:12:19.835 --> 00:12:22.045
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>At this rate. they would have terraformed
our atmosphere in…</i></font>

109
00:12:22.129 --> 00:12:23.797
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. I can do the math. Madam President.</font>

110
00:12:23.881 --> 00:12:27.843
<font color="#FFFFFF">And you can tell the rest of your leaders
that results are on the way.</font>

111
00:12:27.926 --> 00:12:29.178
<font color="#FFFFFF">Bye-bye.</font>

112
00:13:00.250 --> 00:13:01.251
<font color="#FFFFFF">This way. please.</font>

113
00:13:10.761 --> 00:13:12.888
<font color="#FFFFFF">Welcome. welcome.</font>

114
00:13:12.971 --> 00:13:15.724
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't tell you how excited I am
to finally have you here.</font>

115
00:13:15.808 --> 00:13:16.934
<font color="#FFFFFF">You speak English. yes?</font>

116
00:13:17.434 --> 00:13:20.145
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know. we've been trying
to track you down for over a month.</font>

117
00:13:20.229 --> 00:13:24.483
<font color="#FFFFFF">We thought we had you in Kanazawa. but…
You were gone by the time we got there.</font>

118
00:13:24.566 --> 00:13:27.152
<font color="#FFFFFF">Everyone was gone. Everyone but them.</font>

119
00:13:27.236 --> 00:13:30.155
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right. Right. Would you like a drink?
Something to eat?</font>

120
00:13:30.239 --> 00:13:33.534
<font color="#FFFFFF">I have a fabulous chef. He can do Asian.
He can do anything.</font>

121
00:13:34.076 --> 00:13:35.410
<font color="#FFFFFF">What the hell am I doing here?</font>

122
00:13:35.494 --> 00:13:37.538
<font color="#FFFFFF">Oh. Straight to business.</font>

123
00:13:37.621 --> 00:13:38.997
<font color="#FFFFFF">I like it. Okay.</font>

124
00:13:39.998 --> 00:13:42.251
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's get the pleasantries
out of the way. shall we?</font>

125
00:13:43.585 --> 00:13:44.753
<font color="#FFFFFF">My name is Nikhil Kapur.</font>

126
00:13:44.837 --> 00:13:45.838
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know who you are.</font>

127
00:13:47.673 --> 00:13:48.882
<font color="#FFFFFF">Everyone knows who you are.</font>

128
00:13:50.217 --> 00:13:51.593
<font color="#FFFFFF">Right. Right.</font>

129
00:13:51.677 --> 00:13:54.388
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sometimes I forget
there was a world before all this.</font>

130
00:13:55.389 --> 00:13:56.557
<font color="#FFFFFF">Actually. I never forget.</font>

131
00:13:56.640 --> 00:13:58.058
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was just being humble there.</font>

132
00:13:59.101 --> 00:14:01.478
<font color="#FFFFFF">But we don't have time
for false modesty. do we?</font>

133
00:14:01.979 --> 00:14:05.357
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're here because that is here.</font>

134
00:14:05.899 --> 00:14:08.402
<font color="#FFFFFF">And that is here because of you.</font>

135
00:14:09.153 --> 00:14:11.530
<font color="#FFFFFF">It was your codes that made contact
with that ship.</font>

136
00:14:12.948 --> 00:14:15.742
<font color="#FFFFFF">The only communication anyone has made
with the enemy.</font>

137
00:14:17.119 --> 00:14:19.037
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your coordinates made it possible to</font>

138
00:14:20.164 --> 00:14:21.999
<font color="#FFFFFF">shoot that ship out of the sky.</font>

139
00:14:24.751 --> 00:14:26.670
<font color="#FFFFFF">You gave us the only win of this war.</font>

140
00:14:29.965 --> 00:14:30.966
<font color="#FFFFFF">It wasn't a win.</font>

141
00:14:32.551 --> 00:14:34.052
<font color="#FFFFFF">It only made things worse.</font>

142
00:14:37.431 --> 00:14:40.559
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you bring me halfway across the world
to look at a dead ship?</font>

143
00:14:44.271 --> 00:14:45.439
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that what you think?</font>

144
00:14:48.025 --> 00:14:49.026
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's dead?</font>

145
00:14:51.153 --> 00:14:52.613
<font color="#FFFFFF">You communicated with it before.</font>

146
00:14:53.739 --> 00:14:55.574
<font color="#FFFFFF">We want you to communicate with it again.</font>

147
00:14:57.284 --> 00:14:58.285
<font color="#FFFFFF">We've tried.</font>

148
00:14:58.368 --> 00:15:02.206
<font color="#FFFFFF">Had some of the world's greatest minds
in and out of it.</font>

149
00:15:02.289 --> 00:15:05.834
<font color="#FFFFFF">And still. there's only one person
who's ever made contact.</font>

150
00:15:07.711 --> 00:15:08.712
<font color="#FFFFFF">You.</font>

151
00:15:11.089 --> 00:15:15.594
<font color="#FFFFFF">Contact. Communication. Connection.</font>

152
00:15:15.677 --> 00:15:18.680
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's the only chance we'll have
to learn what they want.</font>

153
00:15:19.348 --> 00:15:20.349
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why they're here.</font>

154
00:15:21.016 --> 00:15:22.434
<font color="#FFFFFF">And how to stop them?</font>

155
00:15:26.271 --> 00:15:30.025
<font color="#FFFFFF">The last time I worked with the military.
they lied to me.</font>

156
00:15:31.068 --> 00:15:32.069
<font color="#FFFFFF">They used me.</font>

157
00:15:34.530 --> 00:15:35.656
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why should I trust you?</font>

158
00:15:36.156 --> 00:15:39.368
<font color="#FFFFFF">Because I'm not the military.
and I don't trust them either.</font>

159
00:15:40.661 --> 00:15:43.705
<font color="#FFFFFF">I've worked outside the system
my whole life.</font>

160
00:15:43.789 --> 00:15:46.917
<font color="#FFFFFF">and the only rule I've ever followed is…</font>

161
00:15:49.044 --> 00:15:50.838
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Make sure you're always breaking one."</font>

162
00:15:58.178 --> 00:16:00.848
<font color="#FFFFFF">What did you mean
when you said it's not dead?</font>

163
00:16:03.225 --> 00:16:04.601
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go inside. See for yourself.</font>

164
00:16:05.519 --> 00:16:07.813
<font color="#FFFFFF">We'll just need to run a few tests
on you first.</font>

165
00:16:07.896 --> 00:16:09.606
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What kind of tests?
- Just standard.</font>

166
00:16:09.690 --> 00:16:13.235
<font color="#FFFFFF">To baseline your psychology… physiology…
in case something happens.</font>

167
00:16:13.318 --> 00:16:16.071
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's a formality. really.
for your own safety.</font>

168
00:16:18.949 --> 00:16:19.950
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's in there?</font>

169
00:16:22.327 --> 00:16:25.581
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well. if you can answer that question.
Mitsuki Yamato.</font>

170
00:16:26.540 --> 00:16:29.585
<font color="#FFFFFF">we might actually have a chance
to win this war.</font>

171
00:16:44.516 --> 00:16:47.478
<font color="#FFFFFF">Guys. guys. What are you doing?
I said to pack up. Come on!</font>

172
00:16:47.561 --> 00:16:50.814
<font color="#FFFFFF">I like it here.
We had running water for once.</font>

173
00:16:50.898 --> 00:16:53.609
<font color="#FFFFFF">And mattresses.
even if they're a little stinky.</font>

174
00:16:53.692 --> 00:16:55.569
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's two votes to one. We stay.</font>

175
00:16:55.652 --> 00:16:57.654
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm your mother. It's not a democracy.</font>

176
00:16:57.738 --> 00:17:01.533
<font color="#FFFFFF">It hasn't even been 48 hours yet.
You're not playing by your own rules.</font>

177
00:17:01.617 --> 00:17:04.953
<font color="#FFFFFF">We can't stay because you broke the rules.
It's too dangerous now.</font>

178
00:17:05.037 --> 00:17:07.289
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if that man at the station
called the authorities?</font>

179
00:17:07.372 --> 00:17:09.958
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if there are people looking for us?
We have to keep moving.</font>

180
00:17:10.041 --> 00:17:11.626
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sick of running all the time.</font>

181
00:17:11.710 --> 00:17:14.004
<font color="#FFFFFF">If we go any further.
we're going to drive into the ocean.</font>

182
00:17:14.087 --> 00:17:16.632
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're done heading west. We go north now.</font>

183
00:17:16.714 --> 00:17:19.800
<font color="#FFFFFF">to the top of the continent.
as far as the roads will take us.</font>

184
00:17:19.885 --> 00:17:22.054
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nobody lives that far.
even before the invasion.</font>

185
00:17:22.136 --> 00:17:24.222
<font color="#FFFFFF">Exactly. That's the point.
We will be safe.</font>

186
00:17:24.306 --> 00:17:26.767
<font color="#FFFFFF">From aliens or humans?</font>

187
00:17:33.190 --> 00:17:35.526
<font color="#FFFFFF">It wasn't aliens who took your father.</font>

188
00:17:36.318 --> 00:17:39.655
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please. pack your things. Come on.</font>

189
00:17:56.672 --> 00:17:57.673
<font color="#FFFFFF">Shit.</font>

190
00:17:58.799 --> 00:17:59.967
<font color="#FFFFFF">Looking for this?</font>

191
00:18:03.345 --> 00:18:06.014
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know we don't expose that. ever.</font>

192
00:18:07.182 --> 00:18:09.101
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. give it to me.</font>

193
00:18:09.184 --> 00:18:12.229
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was the one who found it.
It'll keep us safe so we can stay here.</font>

194
00:18:12.312 --> 00:18:14.356
<font color="#FFFFFF">I am the one who keeps us safe. Luke.</font>

195
00:18:14.439 --> 00:18:17.985
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. I said give it to me.
Luke. you need to trust me.</font>

196
00:18:18.068 --> 00:18:20.028
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You need to trust…
- Your little voice inside?</font>

197
00:18:20.112 --> 00:18:22.990
<font color="#FFFFFF">That little voice inside has kept us alive
this whole time.</font>

198
00:18:23.073 --> 00:18:25.534
<font color="#FFFFFF">The whole world out there
is falling apart.</font>

199
00:18:25.617 --> 00:18:27.828
<font color="#FFFFFF">You. your sister.
this family is my whole world.</font>

200
00:18:27.911 --> 00:18:30.372
<font color="#FFFFFF">I would do anything and everything
to hold it together.</font>

201
00:18:30.455 --> 00:18:32.833
<font color="#FFFFFF">You know. I have a voice inside too.
Shouldn't that count?</font>

202
00:18:32.916 --> 00:18:34.168
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes. it should. It should.</font>

203
00:18:34.251 --> 00:18:37.379
<font color="#FFFFFF">When your little voice knows how to drive.
how to cross-stitch a wound in the dark.</font>

204
00:18:37.462 --> 00:18:40.841
<font color="#FFFFFF">how to make a meal out of ration scraps.
how to take care of your sister.</font>

205
00:18:42.634 --> 00:18:46.889
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not only protecting you.
I am preparing you. in case…</font>

206
00:18:46.972 --> 00:18:47.973
<font color="#FFFFFF">In case what?</font>

207
00:18:48.974 --> 00:18:54.438
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. just give it to her. I wanna go now.
Okay? So that's two votes to one.</font>

208
00:18:57.774 --> 00:18:59.526
<font color="#FFFFFF">What if I wanna stay here on my own?</font>

209
00:18:59.610 --> 00:19:01.820
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is not an option.</font>

210
00:19:02.362 --> 00:19:04.490
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where you go. I go. Where I go. you go.</font>

211
00:19:04.573 --> 00:19:06.992
<font color="#FFFFFF">We go together. This is our first rule.</font>

212
00:19:22.508 --> 00:19:23.592
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

213
00:19:27.679 --> 00:19:30.015
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come here. Come here.</font>

214
00:19:38.023 --> 00:19:39.316
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you measuring?</font>

215
00:19:40.108 --> 00:19:42.945
<font color="#FFFFFF">The EEG read is the summation
of the excitatory</font>

216
00:19:43.028 --> 00:19:46.448
<font color="#FFFFFF">and inhibitory potentials
and their constant change.</font>

217
00:19:47.032 --> 00:19:48.033
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you a doctor?</font>

218
00:19:48.575 --> 00:19:50.118
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cognitive scientist.</font>

219
00:19:50.202 --> 00:19:52.412
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll answer all your questions
after the test.</font>

220
00:19:54.581 --> 00:19:55.999
<font color="#FFFFFF">Endo Shusaku.</font>

221
00:19:57.334 --> 00:19:58.585
<font color="#FFFFFF">Enchi Fumiko.</font>

222
00:20:00.838 --> 00:20:04.091
<font color="#FFFFFF">Callas. Clinton.</font>

223
00:20:04.174 --> 00:20:06.468
<font color="#FFFFFF">At what age
did you finish graduate school?</font>

224
00:20:06.552 --> 00:20:07.970
<font color="#FFFFFF">Twenty-two.</font>

225
00:20:09.221 --> 00:20:10.222
<font color="#FFFFFF">The Kremlin.</font>

226
00:20:12.141 --> 00:20:13.142
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mandela.</font>

227
00:20:16.979 --> 00:20:18.480
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know what that is.</font>

228
00:20:18.564 --> 00:20:20.566
<font color="#FFFFFF">First time you fell in love?</font>

229
00:20:24.862 --> 00:20:26.280
<font color="#FFFFFF">First time you fell in love?</font>

230
00:20:28.115 --> 00:20:29.116
<font color="#FFFFFF">Three years ago.</font>

231
00:20:29.908 --> 00:20:31.660
<font color="#FFFFFF">Name of your first love?</font>

232
00:20:34.705 --> 00:20:36.832
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You need to tell me the person's name.
- Why?</font>

233
00:20:37.583 --> 00:20:39.293
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're creating a memory baseline.</font>

234
00:20:39.376 --> 00:20:40.377
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why?</font>

235
00:20:40.961 --> 00:20:42.129
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll explain later.</font>

236
00:20:43.630 --> 00:20:44.631
<font color="#FFFFFF">What was their name?</font>

237
00:20:48.260 --> 00:20:49.261
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hinata.</font>

238
00:20:50.387 --> 00:20:51.680
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is Hinata back in Japan?</font>

239
00:20:52.181 --> 00:20:53.182
<font color="#FFFFFF">No.</font>

240
00:20:57.352 --> 00:20:58.562
<font color="#FFFFFF">Imagine that's your daughter.</font>

241
00:20:58.645 --> 00:21:00.272
<font color="#FFFFFF">Life or death situation.</font>

242
00:21:00.772 --> 00:21:04.902
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you had to save her or Hinata.
who would you choose?</font>

243
00:21:05.861 --> 00:21:07.905
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your lover or the baby?</font>

244
00:21:09.781 --> 00:21:10.782
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lover.</font>

245
00:21:14.286 --> 00:21:16.872
<font color="#FFFFFF">These are sounds recorded
during the collapse of a building.</font>

246
00:21:16.955 --> 00:21:20.292
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you had to save your lover
or your parents. who would you choose?</font>

247
00:21:21.502 --> 00:21:22.503
<font color="#FFFFFF">Lover.</font>

248
00:21:24.296 --> 00:21:27.174
<font color="#FFFFFF">- A line of innocent people…
- Lover. Can we move on?</font>

249
00:21:33.180 --> 00:21:36.350
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Who's with you in the picture?
- My first college roommate.</font>

250
00:21:36.850 --> 00:21:38.018
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ichiko.</font>

251
00:21:53.909 --> 00:21:56.078
<font color="#FFFFFF">That Hinata?</font>

252
00:21:58.163 --> 00:21:59.414
<font color="#FFFFFF">The astronaut?</font>

253
00:21:59.998 --> 00:22:02.960
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is she the reason you were trying
to make contact with the craft?</font>

254
00:22:06.338 --> 00:22:07.840
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Is she the reason you were…
- Yes.</font>

255
00:22:08.507 --> 00:22:10.801
<font color="#FFFFFF">Did you believe Hinata was alive
on that ship?</font>

256
00:22:10.884 --> 00:22:11.969
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is the point of this?</font>

257
00:22:12.052 --> 00:22:14.888
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you feel like you were responsible
for killing Hinata</font>

258
00:22:14.972 --> 00:22:16.890
<font color="#FFFFFF">when that ship was shot out of the sky?</font>

259
00:22:20.727 --> 00:22:24.148
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Do you hold yourself responsible…
- I heard the question. What is your point?</font>

260
00:22:24.231 --> 00:22:26.900
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Do you hold yourself responsible…
- This has nothing to do with…</font>

261
00:22:26.984 --> 00:22:28.360
<font color="#FFFFFF">I need you to answer the question.</font>

262
00:22:28.443 --> 00:22:31.989
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do you hold yourself responsible
for the death of Hinata Murai?</font>

263
00:22:33.490 --> 00:22:34.575
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fuck you.</font>

264
00:22:35.450 --> 00:22:36.493
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that your answer?</font>

265
00:23:28.754 --> 00:23:30.005
<font color="#FFFFFF">"Almond."</font>

266
00:23:36.637 --> 00:23:39.014
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's our key word
for when you're in danger.</font>

267
00:23:44.478 --> 00:23:46.522
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't wanna learn any more Farsi.</font>

268
00:23:47.147 --> 00:23:48.315
<font color="#FFFFFF">We didn't have to before.</font>

269
00:23:48.398 --> 00:23:50.108
<font color="#FFFFFF">- We have to now.
- Why?</font>

270
00:23:50.734 --> 00:23:52.361
<font color="#FFFFFF">It may save our lives one day.</font>

271
00:23:56.406 --> 00:23:57.407
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not good at it.</font>

272
00:24:00.285 --> 00:24:01.495
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's why you practice.</font>

273
00:24:06.124 --> 00:24:07.209
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's it.</font>

274
00:24:12.089 --> 00:24:13.090
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay.</font>

275
00:24:13.173 --> 00:24:16.260
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm going to go inside and ask them
where the next gas station is.</font>

276
00:24:16.343 --> 00:24:17.678
<font color="#FFFFFF">You guys stay here. okay?</font>

277
00:24:17.761 --> 00:24:19.096
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm hungry. Mommy.</font>

278
00:24:19.179 --> 00:24:20.639
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll ask if they have food.</font>

279
00:24:22.057 --> 00:24:23.767
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or we could ask them for some.</font>

280
00:24:33.152 --> 00:24:35.779
<font color="#FFFFFF">We stay away from the military.</font>

281
00:24:36.572 --> 00:24:38.031
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You know the…
- The rules.</font>

282
00:24:39.074 --> 00:24:40.075
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah.</font>

283
00:24:44.079 --> 00:24:45.080
<font color="#FFFFFF">Who do we have?</font>

284
00:24:46.498 --> 00:24:47.499
<font color="#FFFFFF">Each other.</font>

285
00:24:48.750 --> 00:24:49.751
<font color="#FFFFFF">What do we need?</font>

286
00:24:49.835 --> 00:24:51.503
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Nothing else.
- Nothing else.</font>

287
00:24:51.587 --> 00:24:52.588
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's it.</font>

288
00:24:53.422 --> 00:24:54.423
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay.</font>

289
00:24:57.301 --> 00:24:58.719
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll be right back.</font>

290
00:25:31.835 --> 00:25:32.836
<font color="#FFFFFF">Petrol.</font>

291
00:25:35.047 --> 00:25:36.048
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's gas.</font>

292
00:25:40.802 --> 00:25:43.722
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's play a game. I spy.</font>

293
00:25:44.890 --> 00:25:48.685
<font color="#FFFFFF">I spy with my little eye
something beginning with a G?</font>

294
00:25:49.686 --> 00:25:51.772
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. don't go. please.</font>

295
00:25:51.855 --> 00:25:52.856
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll be right back.</font>

296
00:25:53.982 --> 00:25:56.276
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Mom said stay with…
- I heard her. Sarah.</font>

297
00:25:57.611 --> 00:25:59.238
<font color="#FFFFFF">I promise I'll be right back.</font>

298
00:26:24.304 --> 00:26:26.640
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey. Who wants another one?
- I'll take one.</font>

299
00:27:09.850 --> 00:27:11.894
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now. Go now.</font>

300
00:27:46.178 --> 00:27:48.096
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey. kid! What are you doing with that?</font>

301
00:28:00.234 --> 00:28:01.235
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mom.</font>

302
00:28:03.529 --> 00:28:04.530
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mom.</font>

303
00:28:12.496 --> 00:28:13.914
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey. hello.
- Mommy. don't go!</font>

304
00:28:13.997 --> 00:28:15.916
<font color="#FFFFFF">Excuse me. I'm… I'm his mother.</font>

305
00:28:15.999 --> 00:28:18.168
<font color="#FFFFFF">We just ran out of gas.</font>

306
00:28:18.252 --> 00:28:20.420
<font color="#FFFFFF">I went to the store
to ask for the next gas station.</font>

307
00:28:20.504 --> 00:28:26.260
<font color="#FFFFFF">And he clearly did something desperate
and stupid. but he's just a kid</font>

308
00:28:26.343 --> 00:28:27.761
<font color="#FFFFFF">and we're a long way from home.</font>

309
00:28:28.428 --> 00:28:30.013
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sam. put the cans down.</font>

310
00:28:31.515 --> 00:28:34.852
<font color="#FFFFFF">Give them back to these good people
that are keeping us safe</font>

311
00:28:34.935 --> 00:28:36.186
<font color="#FFFFFF">and say you're sorry.</font>

312
00:28:36.270 --> 00:28:37.271
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry.</font>

313
00:28:37.354 --> 00:28:38.772
<font color="#FFFFFF">You see. he's sorry.</font>

314
00:28:39.523 --> 00:28:44.069
<font color="#FFFFFF">Kids make mistakes. but I assure you.
he's not going to make this one again.</font>

315
00:28:44.153 --> 00:28:46.530
<font color="#FFFFFF">You wouldn't happen
to be with the Movement. would you?</font>

316
00:28:47.030 --> 00:28:48.115
<font color="#FFFFFF">The what?</font>

317
00:28:48.615 --> 00:28:52.244
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know what you're talking about.
We're a family. He's just a child.</font>

318
00:28:52.744 --> 00:28:54.746
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then you won't mind if we check your car.</font>

319
00:28:54.830 --> 00:28:56.832
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like you said.
our job is to keep people safe.</font>

320
00:28:58.417 --> 00:29:00.002
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're just going to scare the kids.</font>

321
00:29:00.085 --> 00:29:02.963
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your boy should've thought of that before
he tried to steal government property.</font>

322
00:29:03.046 --> 00:29:04.047
<font color="#FFFFFF">ma'am.</font>

323
00:29:05.549 --> 00:29:06.884
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hands up.
- What?</font>

324
00:29:06.967 --> 00:29:09.636
<font color="#FFFFFF">I asked you to raise your hands
so I can check you for weapons.</font>

325
00:29:09.720 --> 00:29:11.889
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I'm a mother.
- You'd be surprised what we've seen.</font>

326
00:29:11.972 --> 00:29:15.350
<font color="#FFFFFF">- No. I wouldn't.
- Gun! Got a gun here.</font>

327
00:29:20.063 --> 00:29:21.857
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Search their car.
- Yes. sir.</font>

328
00:29:22.441 --> 00:29:24.985
<font color="#FFFFFF">That gun was for protection.
to defend my family.</font>

329
00:29:25.068 --> 00:29:26.236
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please. just let us go.</font>

330
00:29:26.320 --> 00:29:28.030
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Sam. say you're sorry.
- Sorry.</font>

331
00:29:28.113 --> 00:29:29.781
<font color="#FFFFFF">- He said that already.
- Just…</font>

332
00:29:30.991 --> 00:29:32.117
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Mommy!
- Hey!</font>

333
00:29:32.201 --> 00:29:34.286
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Mommy!
- Don't touch her. Don't touch her!</font>

334
00:29:34.369 --> 00:29:37.122
<font color="#FFFFFF">Listen. just take the gun. Keep it. okay?</font>

335
00:29:37.206 --> 00:29:38.582
<font color="#FFFFFF">Just let us go. I beg you.</font>

336
00:29:38.665 --> 00:29:40.667
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're just a family trying to survive!</font>

337
00:29:41.168 --> 00:29:43.712
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm sorry. It's all my fault.
Please. just… I'm sorry.</font>

338
00:29:43.795 --> 00:29:45.923
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Cap!
- Please. just don't hurt us.</font>

339
00:29:46.006 --> 00:29:47.633
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let us go. Okay?</font>

340
00:29:47.716 --> 00:29:48.759
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please. just stop.</font>

341
00:29:49.426 --> 00:29:50.427
<font color="#FFFFFF">Please.</font>

342
00:29:55.432 --> 00:29:57.309
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What is this?
- I don't know.</font>

343
00:30:01.063 --> 00:30:02.231
<font color="#FFFFFF">What is your name?</font>

344
00:30:04.650 --> 00:30:06.026
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ana Lewis.</font>

345
00:30:09.071 --> 00:30:10.823
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get the electromagnetic field meter.</font>

346
00:30:11.365 --> 00:30:12.366
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes. sir.</font>

347
00:30:14.409 --> 00:30:16.662
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're on the lookout
for a lot of things these days.</font>

348
00:30:16.745 --> 00:30:19.915
<font color="#FFFFFF">But one of them is a family with something
the government thinks could be a weapon</font>

349
00:30:19.998 --> 00:30:21.208
<font color="#FFFFFF">against the aliens.</font>

350
00:30:21.291 --> 00:30:23.335
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know what you're talking about.</font>

351
00:30:23.836 --> 00:30:25.462
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is just a piece of metal.</font>

352
00:30:33.554 --> 00:30:34.763
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cap.</font>

353
00:30:40.394 --> 00:30:41.603
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aneesha.</font>

354
00:30:44.523 --> 00:30:45.524
<font color="#FFFFFF">Aneesha Malik.</font>

355
00:30:50.571 --> 00:30:53.115
<font color="#FFFFFF">Load them and all their things
into the convoy.</font>

356
00:30:54.366 --> 00:30:55.909
<font color="#FFFFFF">All right. Be gentle with her.</font>

357
00:31:06.086 --> 00:31:07.296
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come here.</font>

358
00:31:17.139 --> 00:31:18.432
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fall in!</font>

359
00:31:18.515 --> 00:31:19.600
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hello.</font>

360
00:31:19.683 --> 00:31:21.393
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's move it!</font>

361
00:31:21.477 --> 00:31:23.604
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's go. Hurry up. Hurry up.</font>

362
00:31:23.687 --> 00:31:25.272
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't need to be afraid.</font>

363
00:31:25.355 --> 00:31:27.024
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's move. Let's go!</font>

364
00:31:27.107 --> 00:31:28.400
<font color="#FFFFFF">At least not of me.</font>

365
00:31:28.901 --> 00:31:30.110
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's go!</font>

366
00:31:35.407 --> 00:31:37.534
<font color="#FFFFFF">She failed the test.</font>

367
00:31:37.618 --> 00:31:38.619
<font color="#FFFFFF">Badly.</font>

368
00:31:39.411 --> 00:31:41.246
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's easily overstimulated.</font>

369
00:31:41.330 --> 00:31:44.082
<font color="#FFFFFF">goes into fight-or-flight mode
in a matter of nanoseconds.</font>

370
00:31:44.583 --> 00:31:47.002
<font color="#FFFFFF">and her response time
is the quickest I've seen.</font>

371
00:31:47.085 --> 00:31:48.837
<font color="#FFFFFF">Also the most reckless.</font>

372
00:31:48.921 --> 00:31:52.299
<font color="#FFFFFF">Well. I think we could use
a little recklessness at this point.</font>

373
00:31:53.926 --> 00:31:56.553
<font color="#FFFFFF">Progress requires radical thinking.</font>

374
00:31:57.888 --> 00:31:59.181
<font color="#FFFFFF">Be that as it may.</font>

375
00:31:59.264 --> 00:32:02.643
<font color="#FFFFFF">you know what happened to the scientists
with stable baselines who went in there.</font>

376
00:32:02.726 --> 00:32:04.353
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. yeah. they gave us nothing.</font>

377
00:32:04.895 --> 00:32:06.730
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm talking about what happened to them.</font>

378
00:32:06.814 --> 00:32:08.357
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know what you're talking about.</font>

379
00:32:09.525 --> 00:32:12.486
<font color="#FFFFFF">But she might be my best chance
of saving the species.</font>

380
00:32:13.320 --> 00:32:14.404
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your best chance?</font>

381
00:32:15.197 --> 00:32:16.323
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good. good.</font>

382
00:32:16.406 --> 00:32:19.326
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't pay you to psychoanalyze me.</font>

383
00:32:19.409 --> 00:32:20.702
<font color="#FFFFFF">So save it for the job.</font>

384
00:32:22.037 --> 00:32:25.374
<font color="#FFFFFF">Look. she's the reason that thing's
sitting here in the Amazon</font>

385
00:32:25.999 --> 00:32:27.292
<font color="#FFFFFF">instead of up in space.</font>

386
00:32:27.376 --> 00:32:30.045
<font color="#FFFFFF">Which she doesn't see
as the same victory you do.</font>

387
00:32:30.838 --> 00:32:34.383
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nikhil. this woman wasn't just
out in the field saving lives.</font>

388
00:32:35.175 --> 00:32:37.511
<font color="#FFFFFF">She was out there to atone for taking one.</font>

389
00:32:39.179 --> 00:32:42.141
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's operating
from a place of anger and guilt.</font>

390
00:32:42.224 --> 00:32:44.518
<font color="#FFFFFF">which are two
of the most volatile motivators.</font>

391
00:32:44.601 --> 00:32:48.272
<font color="#FFFFFF">You put her in that ship. and there's
no way to predict how she'll act or react.</font>

392
00:32:49.690 --> 00:32:52.651
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't care about her?
Think about the mission.</font>

393
00:32:53.902 --> 00:32:55.028
<font color="#FFFFFF">Your mission.</font>

394
00:32:57.281 --> 00:32:59.074
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay. let's go tell her.</font>

395
00:33:25.601 --> 00:33:29.396
<font color="#FFFFFF">So. Dr. Castillo says
you failed the tests.</font>

396
00:33:29.480 --> 00:33:31.648
<font color="#FFFFFF">At least the ones you cared to complete.</font>

397
00:33:31.732 --> 00:33:35.319
<font color="#FFFFFF">She says you're not psychologically stable
enough to go inside the ship.</font>

398
00:33:35.402 --> 00:33:38.280
<font color="#FFFFFF">which is why Dr. Castillo
will be accompanying you into the ship.</font>

399
00:33:38.363 --> 00:33:39.740
<font color="#FFFFFF">- What?
- No.</font>

400
00:33:39.823 --> 00:33:42.576
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. I know you two
got off to a rocky start.</font>

401
00:33:42.659 --> 00:33:44.077
<font color="#FFFFFF">Had a bit of a ding-dong. didn't you?</font>

402
00:33:44.161 --> 00:33:48.081
<font color="#FFFFFF">So you may not feel
all warm and fuzzy about this.</font>

403
00:33:48.165 --> 00:33:51.168
<font color="#FFFFFF">but I'm a big believer
in not caring how people feel.</font>

404
00:33:51.668 --> 00:33:53.504
<font color="#FFFFFF">Feelings get in the way.</font>

405
00:33:54.129 --> 00:33:56.924
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's really one of the great failings
of our species.</font>

406
00:33:57.424 --> 00:33:59.843
<font color="#FFFFFF">and may well be why we're losing this war.</font>

407
00:33:59.927 --> 00:34:03.722
<font color="#FFFFFF">So. with that in mind. I'm ask…
Well. really. telling both of you</font>

408
00:34:03.806 --> 00:34:07.768
<font color="#FFFFFF">to put whatever feelings you have aside.</font>

409
00:34:08.392 --> 00:34:13.482
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go inside that ship
to see if you can make some magic again.</font>

410
00:34:15.108 --> 00:34:17.026
<font color="#FFFFFF">You got into their hive mind once.</font>

411
00:34:18.070 --> 00:34:19.821
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm betting you can do it again.</font>

412
00:34:19.905 --> 00:34:25.077
<font color="#FFFFFF">And to help cover that bet.
Maya will be there to monitor your mind.</font>

413
00:34:25.577 --> 00:34:26.662
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't need a monitor.</font>

414
00:34:26.745 --> 00:34:27.745
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes. you do.</font>

415
00:34:28.455 --> 00:34:31.792
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maya's job is to map traces
of consciousness inside the ship.</font>

416
00:34:31.875 --> 00:34:35.796
<font color="#FFFFFF">She can map your consciousness
and make sure you remain stable.</font>

417
00:34:35.879 --> 00:34:37.506
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or as stable as your baseline.</font>

418
00:34:37.589 --> 00:34:40.175
<font color="#FFFFFF">which. as we've established.
is not very stable.</font>

419
00:34:40.259 --> 00:34:41.635
<font color="#FFFFFF">Great. That's settled then.</font>

420
00:34:41.718 --> 00:34:44.638
<font color="#FFFFFF">So. should we stand here
while the world's burning?</font>

421
00:34:45.138 --> 00:34:48.183
<font color="#FFFFFF">Or should we get you
suited and booted to help save it?</font>

422
00:35:00.028 --> 00:35:01.405
<font color="#FFFFFF">Watch your step.</font>

423
00:35:11.957 --> 00:35:13.876
<font color="#FFFFFF">The suit is coded to your biometrics.</font>

424
00:35:14.877 --> 00:35:16.795
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'll be monitoring your vitals
at all times.</font>

425
00:35:18.505 --> 00:35:21.425
<font color="#FFFFFF">If you detect any malfunction.
abort the mission.</font>

426
00:35:54.750 --> 00:35:57.544
<font color="#FFFFFF">Word spreads fast.
They know you're going in.</font>

427
00:36:00.464 --> 00:36:01.507
<font color="#FFFFFF">Maya.</font>

428
00:36:02.299 --> 00:36:03.842
<font color="#FFFFFF">You good?</font>

429
00:36:03.884 --> 00:36:05.636
<font color="#FFFFFF">We delivered the samples
to your lab. okay?</font>

430
00:36:05.719 --> 00:36:06.720
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.</font>

431
00:36:06.804 --> 00:36:09.181
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mitsuki Yamato.
meet Tomas. our lead chemist</font>

432
00:36:09.264 --> 00:36:11.016
<font color="#FFFFFF">and master sample collector.</font>

433
00:36:11.099 --> 00:36:12.976
<font color="#FFFFFF">Welcome to the belly of the whale.</font>

434
00:36:16.355 --> 00:36:18.732
<font color="#FFFFFF">The walls have
microscopic neural pathways.</font>

435
00:36:19.233 --> 00:36:21.401
<font color="#FFFFFF">The ship is like an operational limb.</font>

436
00:36:22.611 --> 00:36:24.696
<font color="#FFFFFF">which is why we can study
how it transmits data.</font>

437
00:36:24.780 --> 00:36:26.323
<font color="#FFFFFF">She's going in?</font>

438
00:36:26.365 --> 00:36:28.367
<font color="#FFFFFF">Nikhil approved it.</font>

439
00:36:30.327 --> 00:36:33.664
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's his world.
and we're just living or dying in it.</font>

440
00:36:34.414 --> 00:36:35.666
<font color="#FFFFFF">This way.</font>

441
00:36:58.313 --> 00:36:59.481
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are these?</font>

442
00:37:02.276 --> 00:37:03.527
<font color="#FFFFFF">Drop-ships.</font>

443
00:37:04.153 --> 00:37:06.697
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's how the first wave of aliens
came to Earth.</font>

444
00:37:07.781 --> 00:37:08.782
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cloaked.</font>

445
00:37:09.700 --> 00:37:11.493
<font color="#FFFFFF">That's why we never saw them coming.</font>

446
00:37:12.703 --> 00:37:14.454
<font color="#FFFFFF">We still don't see them coming.</font>

447
00:37:17.833 --> 00:37:19.585
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're hoping you can help with that.</font>

448
00:37:36.977 --> 00:37:38.604
<font color="#FFFFFF">My name is Clark. by the way.</font>

449
00:37:43.859 --> 00:37:45.027
<font color="#FFFFFF">And you are?</font>

450
00:37:45.527 --> 00:37:47.821
<font color="#FFFFFF">We don't talk to strangers.</font>

451
00:37:48.405 --> 00:37:50.574
<font color="#FFFFFF">I'm not a stranger.
I just told you my name.</font>

452
00:37:57.498 --> 00:37:58.832
<font color="#FFFFFF">Where are they taking us?</font>

453
00:38:02.169 --> 00:38:04.087
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not far. I can tell you that.</font>

454
00:38:07.633 --> 00:38:09.718
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're very calm for a man in handcuffs.</font>

455
00:38:10.677 --> 00:38:13.055
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hardest prison to escape is your own mind.</font>

456
00:38:17.100 --> 00:38:18.977
<font color="#FFFFFF">Sorry. I was</font>

457
00:38:19.895 --> 00:38:21.814
<font color="#FFFFFF">a English teacher in the before times.</font>

458
00:38:22.689 --> 00:38:23.690
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mom?</font>

459
00:38:25.359 --> 00:38:26.652
<font color="#FFFFFF">What are you now?</font>

460
00:38:26.735 --> 00:38:27.736
<font color="#FFFFFF">Same as you.</font>

461
00:38:28.278 --> 00:38:29.321
<font color="#FFFFFF">A survivor.</font>

462
00:38:30.489 --> 00:38:33.116
<font color="#FFFFFF">And if you wanna stay that way.
I suggest you trust me.</font>

463
00:38:36.703 --> 00:38:37.830
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why?</font>

464
00:38:37.913 --> 00:38:40.707
<font color="#FFFFFF">The definition of trust requires you
to relinquish that word.</font>

465
00:38:42.876 --> 00:38:45.170
<font color="#FFFFFF">But I guess you could say the answer is…</font>

466
00:38:47.339 --> 00:38:48.924
<font color="#FFFFFF">'cause I'm not really a prisoner here.</font>

467
00:38:54.096 --> 00:38:55.806
<font color="#FFFFFF">Not everything is what it seems.</font>

468
00:39:16.201 --> 00:39:17.744
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on. She looks hurt.</font>

469
00:39:17.828 --> 00:39:20.455
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey. kid. are you okay?
- What happened to you?</font>

470
00:39:20.539 --> 00:39:22.207
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're gonna be all right.</font>

471
00:39:24.251 --> 00:39:25.252
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's okay.</font>

472
00:39:29.464 --> 00:39:30.883
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Hey. Hey. hey!
- All right. Okay.</font>

473
00:39:30.966 --> 00:39:33.385
<font color="#FFFFFF">- You lie down. Get down!
- Hey!</font>

474
00:39:34.887 --> 00:39:37.389
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Out of the truck!
- Get on the ground!</font>

475
00:39:38.807 --> 00:39:39.975
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's going on?</font>

476
00:39:40.058 --> 00:39:41.894
<font color="#FFFFFF">Stay calm and stay behind me.</font>

477
00:39:45.814 --> 00:39:50.319
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Yeah. yeah. yeah. Sit tight!
- On the ground. face down!</font>

478
00:39:51.737 --> 00:39:53.864
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hey. give us the zip ties.</font>

479
00:39:56.200 --> 00:39:58.327
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do it! Now!</font>

480
00:40:01.205 --> 00:40:02.748
<font color="#FFFFFF">I got you. You're gonna be okay.</font>

481
00:40:07.711 --> 00:40:09.171
<font color="#FFFFFF">Cover your ears.</font>

482
00:40:15.177 --> 00:40:17.596
<font color="#FFFFFF">Watch yourselves! Fire in the hole!</font>

483
00:40:25.521 --> 00:40:27.231
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come with us. Come on.</font>

484
00:40:29.483 --> 00:40:30.567
<font color="#FFFFFF">Trust me.</font>

485
00:40:43.121 --> 00:40:44.122
<font color="#FFFFFF">They called it in!</font>

486
00:40:47.251 --> 00:40:48.544
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to move out!</font>

487
00:40:50.420 --> 00:40:51.421
<font color="#FFFFFF">Now or never.</font>

488
00:40:52.548 --> 00:40:53.757
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mom.</font>

489
00:40:56.134 --> 00:40:58.095
<font color="#FFFFFF">We need to get the things
they took from us.</font>

490
00:40:58.178 --> 00:40:59.972
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get their things. Everything.</font>

491
00:41:00.055 --> 00:41:01.390
<font color="#FFFFFF">Come on.</font>

492
00:41:06.603 --> 00:41:09.898
<font color="#FFFFFF">On the hunt! On the hunt!
Get in the truck.</font>

493
00:41:09.982 --> 00:41:11.775
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Get off.
- Hustle!</font>

494
00:41:11.859 --> 00:41:14.236
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay. let's go. Go. go. go!</font>

495
00:41:21.451 --> 00:41:22.744
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fall in!</font>

496
00:41:26.081 --> 00:41:28.000
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're fighting a war
against the same enemy.</font>

497
00:41:28.667 --> 00:41:31.879
<font color="#FFFFFF">You guys start acting that way.
maybe it's a war that we can win.</font>

498
00:41:32.671 --> 00:41:33.964
<font color="#FFFFFF">Take the bags!</font>

499
00:41:34.047 --> 00:41:36.049
<font color="#FFFFFF">Leave their coats. Keep 'em warm.</font>

500
00:41:39.303 --> 00:41:41.722
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's go! Let's go!</font>

501
00:41:41.805 --> 00:41:43.557
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. that front one right there.</font>

502
00:41:45.225 --> 00:41:46.602
<font color="#FFFFFF">Do final checks here.</font>

503
00:41:48.604 --> 00:41:50.439
<font color="#FFFFFF">- All right. let's go!
- Come on!</font>

504
00:41:54.318 --> 00:41:56.195
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good work. Let's go.</font>

505
00:41:59.198 --> 00:42:00.199
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay. let's go!</font>

506
00:42:00.282 --> 00:42:01.658
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Ryder.
- Dad.</font>

507
00:42:02.701 --> 00:42:03.702
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good work.</font>

508
00:42:04.620 --> 00:42:05.996
<font color="#FFFFFF">Load it up. here.</font>

509
00:42:06.872 --> 00:42:08.207
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pack it up.</font>

510
00:42:08.290 --> 00:42:09.291
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you okay?</font>

511
00:42:09.374 --> 00:42:10.667
<font color="#FFFFFF">Pack up! Let's go!</font>

512
00:42:10.751 --> 00:42:12.628
<font color="#FFFFFF">Good old-fashioned Heinz 57.</font>

513
00:42:20.928 --> 00:42:21.929
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's go!</font>

514
00:42:22.888 --> 00:42:23.889
<font color="#FFFFFF">Like I said.</font>

515
00:42:24.598 --> 00:42:26.141
<font color="#FFFFFF">not everything is what it seems.</font>

516
00:42:50.916 --> 00:42:52.000
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here we are.</font>

517
00:43:19.820 --> 00:43:22.489
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. It's bigger than Canada in there.</font>

518
00:43:31.915 --> 00:43:32.916
<font color="#FFFFFF">You saw it?</font>

519
00:43:37.713 --> 00:43:38.964
<font color="#FFFFFF">You have live video?</font>

520
00:43:39.756 --> 00:43:41.884
<font color="#FFFFFF">No. it distorts the feed.</font>

521
00:43:48.348 --> 00:43:49.600
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's in there?</font>

522
00:43:50.434 --> 00:43:52.269
<font color="#FFFFFF">An enormous power source.</font>

523
00:43:53.270 --> 00:43:55.647
<font color="#FFFFFF">But we can't get past her
to find out what.</font>

524
00:43:57.483 --> 00:43:58.775
<font color="#FFFFFF">Her?</font>

525
00:44:02.321 --> 00:44:03.447
<font color="#FFFFFF">Follow me.</font>

526
00:44:39.191 --> 00:44:42.277
<font color="#FFFFFF">You should know. everyone who's
entered this room suffered memory loss.</font>

527
00:44:42.861 --> 00:44:46.365
<font color="#FFFFFF">And the last person to go in
suffered severe neurological damage.</font>

528
00:44:48.200 --> 00:44:49.701
<font color="#FFFFFF">What sort of damage?</font>

529
00:44:50.244 --> 00:44:51.370
<font color="#FFFFFF">I don't know yet.</font>

530
00:44:52.079 --> 00:44:53.914
<font color="#FFFFFF">He hasn't regained consciousness.</font>

531
00:45:00.045 --> 00:45:02.089
<font color="#FFFFFF">I wasn't trying to hurt you
with that test.</font>

532
00:45:03.257 --> 00:45:04.758
<font color="#FFFFFF">I was trying to help you.</font>

533
00:45:13.183 --> 00:45:14.726
<font color="#FFFFFF">Are you sure you want to do this?</font>

534
00:45:16.770 --> 00:45:17.771
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes.</font>

535
00:45:19.815 --> 00:45:21.441
<font color="#FFFFFF">Protocol is 15 minutes and out.</font>

536
00:45:21.525 --> 00:45:23.485
<font color="#FFFFFF">Higher functions check every two minutes.</font>

537
00:45:24.820 --> 00:45:25.821
<font color="#FFFFFF">Got it.</font>

538
00:45:26.405 --> 00:45:28.699
<font color="#FFFFFF">I can't guarantee
you won't forget your mother's face</font>

539
00:45:28.782 --> 00:45:30.784
<font color="#FFFFFF">or the taste of your favorite food.</font>

540
00:45:31.285 --> 00:45:32.411
<font color="#FFFFFF">I said I got it.</font>

541
00:45:34.329 --> 00:45:35.622
<font color="#FFFFFF">Okay.</font>

542
00:45:46.758 --> 00:45:47.843
<font color="#FFFFFF">Tether port.</font>

543
00:45:48.844 --> 00:45:50.429
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Tether connected.</i></font>

544
00:45:50.512 --> 00:45:53.265
<font color="#FFFFFF">Press this
if you need emergency extraction.</font>

545
00:45:53.348 --> 00:45:54.808
<font color="#FFFFFF">In case you can't speak.</font>

546
00:45:57.352 --> 00:45:58.520
<font color="#FFFFFF">Helmet on.</font>

547
00:46:19.333 --> 00:46:20.792
<font color="#FFFFFF">Showtime.</font>

548
00:46:29.259 --> 00:46:31.261
<font color="#FFFFFF">Why don't you tell us where we're going?</font>

549
00:46:31.345 --> 00:46:34.515
<font color="#FFFFFF">Told you already. Somewhere safe. warm.</font>

550
00:46:35.307 --> 00:46:36.558
<font color="#FFFFFF">Get some food and sleep.</font>

551
00:46:37.851 --> 00:46:38.852
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then we keep moving.</font>

552
00:46:38.936 --> 00:46:41.230
<font color="#FFFFFF">Thank you.
but we will just get our things and go.</font>

553
00:46:42.022 --> 00:46:43.482
<font color="#FFFFFF">That wouldn't be wise.</font>

554
00:46:44.274 --> 00:46:46.610
<font color="#FFFFFF">Then again. you were in the back
of that military van.</font>

555
00:46:47.110 --> 00:46:48.487
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know who you people are.</font>

556
00:46:50.572 --> 00:46:52.115
<font color="#FFFFFF">The orange colors.</font>

557
00:46:53.534 --> 00:46:55.577
<font color="#FFFFFF">You call yourself "the Movement."</font>

558
00:46:57.037 --> 00:46:58.580
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Anarchists.
- Activists.</font>

559
00:46:58.664 --> 00:47:01.500
<font color="#FFFFFF">We don't want any trouble.
We just want our things.</font>

560
00:47:04.419 --> 00:47:06.880
<font color="#FFFFFF">- I mean. it's cold out there. Mom.
- Doesn't matter.</font>

561
00:47:08.382 --> 00:47:09.842
<font color="#FFFFFF">Mom. I'm hungry.</font>

562
00:47:10.717 --> 00:47:12.135
<font color="#FFFFFF">Comin' up.</font>

563
00:47:21.353 --> 00:47:22.771
<font color="#FFFFFF">The gate!</font>

564
00:47:27.651 --> 00:47:28.861
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's go!</font>

565
00:47:43.292 --> 00:47:44.501
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hold!</font>

566
00:48:02.186 --> 00:48:03.854
<font color="#FFFFFF">We're the only warm place for miles.</font>

567
00:48:04.855 --> 00:48:07.274
<font color="#FFFFFF">I know because we scouted
the next 50 miles.</font>

568
00:48:07.357 --> 00:48:08.817
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's what we do.</font>

569
00:48:09.318 --> 00:48:12.070
<font color="#FFFFFF">Help people. Keep them safe.</font>

570
00:48:13.739 --> 00:48:15.115
<font color="#FFFFFF">People like you.</font>

571
00:48:16.033 --> 00:48:18.452
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here you go. All your stuff.</font>

572
00:48:21.497 --> 00:48:23.916
<font color="#FFFFFF">- Thank you.
- You can get a good night's sleep.</font>

573
00:48:23.999 --> 00:48:27.252
<font color="#FFFFFF">and we'll take you to the closest refugee
camp in the morning. How's that sound?</font>

574
00:48:27.336 --> 00:48:29.087
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that hot chocolate?</font>

575
00:48:29.588 --> 00:48:31.757
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yes. it is hot chocolate. You want some?</font>

576
00:48:38.555 --> 00:48:42.017
<font color="#FFFFFF">You're one of those who thinks it's safer
not to make any connections.</font>

577
00:48:42.100 --> 00:48:43.477
<font color="#FFFFFF">The truth is the opposite.</font>

578
00:48:45.354 --> 00:48:47.564
<font color="#FFFFFF">Connections are the only thing
keeping us alive.</font>

579
00:48:57.282 --> 00:48:59.493
<font color="#FFFFFF">Go get some hot chocolate. Go.</font>

580
00:49:40.284 --> 00:49:41.493
<font color="#FFFFFF">Here we go.</font>

581
00:50:03.515 --> 00:50:05.267
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Yamato. check-in.</i></font>

582
00:50:05.350 --> 00:50:09.313
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>First phone number. College roommate.
What color are my eyes?</i></font>

583
00:50:10.397 --> 00:50:14.985
<font color="#FFFFFF">02-555-0876.</font>

584
00:50:15.068 --> 00:50:16.320
<font color="#FFFFFF">Ichiko. Green.</font>

585
00:50:16.403 --> 00:50:19.031
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Good. good. You're doing great.</i></font>

586
00:50:20.616 --> 00:50:23.035
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>Tracking neurological activity
throughout the ship.</i></font>

587
00:50:23.744 --> 00:50:27.372
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>All the frequencies you requested
are loaded onto your wrist interface.</i></font>

588
00:50:46.725 --> 00:50:48.143
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's responding to her.</font>

589
00:50:51.104 --> 00:50:52.105
<font color="#FFFFFF">This is crazy.</font>

590
00:50:54.066 --> 00:50:56.401
<font color="#FFFFFF">What the hell…?</font>

591
00:51:43.157 --> 00:51:44.241
<font color="#FFFFFF"><i>What the hell's happening?</i></font>

592
00:51:46.368 --> 00:51:48.495
<font color="#FFFFFF">- It's almost time to pull her out.
- No.</font>

593
00:51:48.579 --> 00:51:50.372
<font color="#FFFFFF">Fifteen minutes and out. It's protocol.</font>

594
00:51:50.873 --> 00:51:52.332
<font color="#FFFFFF">To hell with protocol.</font>

595
00:51:52.875 --> 00:51:56.003
<font color="#FFFFFF">If we sever this connection now.
we may never get it back.</font>

596
00:51:56.086 --> 00:51:57.212
<font color="#FFFFFF">You don't know that.</font>

597
00:51:57.296 --> 00:51:59.381
<font color="#FFFFFF">If we leave her in there.
we might not get her back.</font>

598
00:51:59.464 --> 00:52:01.008
<font color="#FFFFFF">Yeah. that's an acceptable risk.</font>

599
00:52:01.717 --> 00:52:05.012
<font color="#FFFFFF">- It's not your risk.
- She stays in until this connection breaks</font>

600
00:52:05.512 --> 00:52:06.680
<font color="#FFFFFF">or she does.</font>

601
00:52:21.278 --> 00:52:23.655
<font color="#FFFFFF">Let's try this.</font>

602
00:53:15.123 --> 00:53:16.250
<font color="#FFFFFF">Is that…</font>

603
00:54:38.165 --> 00:54:39.291
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke.</font>

604
00:54:40.626 --> 00:54:41.627
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke.</font>

605
00:54:45.714 --> 00:54:46.924
<font color="#FFFFFF">Luke. what is it?</font>

606
00:54:47.591 --> 00:54:48.926
<font color="#FFFFFF">Can you hear that?</font>

607
00:54:54.807 --> 00:54:56.308
<font color="#FFFFFF">Hear what?</font>

608
00:54:57.935 --> 00:54:58.936
<font color="#FFFFFF">That…</font>

609
00:55:01.605 --> 00:55:02.731
<font color="#FFFFFF">humming.</font>

610
00:55:32.845 --> 00:55:34.429
<font color="#FFFFFF">What's going on?</font>

611
00:55:34.471 --> 00:55:36.140
<font color="#FFFFFF">It started a few moments ago.</font>

612
00:55:36.181 --> 00:55:40.018
<font color="#FFFFFF">I thought it was just another tremor. like
the others. But the others were random.</font>

613
00:55:55.409 --> 00:55:58.203
<font color="#FFFFFF">This tremor is rhythmic. It has a pattern.</font>

614
00:56:00.914 --> 00:56:03.250
<font color="#FFFFFF">It's different this time.</font>

615
00:56:03.959 --> 00:56:06.295
<font color="#FFFFFF">Something's changed.</font>

616
